        </li>
        <li>
          <a class="social" href="https://www.instagram.com/apolloniaspace/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2.2c3.2 0 3.6 0 4.8.1 1.2.1 1.8.2 2.2.4.6.2 1 .5 1.4.9.4.4.7.8.9 1.4.2.4.4 1.1.4 2.2.1 1.3.1 1.6.1 4.8s0 3.6-.1 4.8c-.1 1.2-.2 1.8-.4 2.2-.2.6-.5 1-.9 1.4-.4.4-.8.7-1.4.9-.4.2-1.1.4-2.2.4-1.3.1-1.6.1-4.8.1s-3.6 0-4.8-.1c-1.2-.1-1.8-.2-2.2-.4-.6-.2-1-.5-1.4-.9-.4-.4-.7-.8-.9-1.4-.2-.4-.4-1.1-.4-2.2-.1-1.3-.1-1.6-.1-4.8s0-3.6.1-4.8c.1-1.2.2-1.8.4-2.2.2-.6.5-1 .9-1.4.4-.4.8-.7 1.4-.9.4-.2 1.1-.4 2.2-.4 1.2-.1 1.6-.1 4.8-.1zM12 0C8.7 0 8.3 0 7.1.1 5.8.1 4.9.3 4.1.6c-.8.3-1.5.7-2.2 1.4C1.2 2.6.8 3.3.5 4.1.2 4.9.1 5.8 0 7.1 0 8.3 0 8.7 0 12s0 3.7.1 4.9c.1 1.3.2 2.2.5 2.9.3.8.7 1.5 1.4 2.2.7.7 1.4 1.1 2.2 1.4.8.3 1.6.5 2.9.5C8.3 24 8.7 24 12 24s3.7 0 4.9-.1c1.3-.1 2.2-.2 2.9-.5.8-.3 1.5-.7 2.2-1.4.7-.7 1.1-1.4 1.4-2.2.3-.8.5-1.6.5-2.9.1-1.2.1-1.6.1-4.9s0-3.7-.1-4.9c-.1-1.3-.2-2.2-.5-2.9-.3-.8-.7-1.5-1.4-2.2-.7-.7-1.4-1.1-2.2-1.4-.7-.3-1.6-.5-2.9-.5C15.7 0 15.3 0 12 0zm0 5.8a6.2 6.2 0 1 0 0 12.4 6.2 6.2 0 0 0 0-12.4zM12 16a4 4 0 1 1 0-8 4 4 0 0 1 0 8zm6.4-10.8a1.4 1.4 0 1 0 0 2.8 1.4 1.4 0 0 0 0-2.8z"/></svg>
            Instagram
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a class="social" href="https://substack.com/@apolloniaspace" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22.539 8.242H1.46V5.406h21.08v2.836zM1.46 10.812V24L12 18.11 22.54 24V10.812H1.46zM22.54 0H1.46v2.836h21.08V0z"/></svg>
            Substack
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a class="social" href="https://www.youtube.com/@ApolloniaSpace" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M23.5 6.2a3 3 0 0 0-2.1-2.1C19.5 3.5 12 3.5 12 3.5s-7.5 0-9.4.6A3 3 0 0 0 .5 6.2 31.5 31.5 0 0 0 0 12a31.5 31.5 0 0 0 .5 5.8 3 3 0 0 0 2.1 2.1c1.9.6 9.4.6 9.4.6s7.5 0 9.4-.6a3 3 0 0 0 2.1-2.1A31.5 31.5 0 0 0 24 12a31.5 31.5 0 0 0-.5-5.8zM9.5 15.6V8.4l6.3 3.6-6.3 3.6z"/></svg>
